          "author_url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohammad-mahdi-khadem-al-charieh-bb80aa227",
          "text": "The biggest challenge of building large projects is figuring out what the customer actually needs, formalizing that in precise language and properly communicating it.\nThat is what the picture is trying to convey.\nAnd that is exactly the opposite of what AI is good at.\n\nAI will make these issues worse, ship more of what people ask for and less of what they actually need.\nI guess you could say AI does at least help you fail faster and find issues in the requirements earlier.",
